Texts.Chs:
尽管拥有蓬松的外观，这个种族却具有极强的适应性。
他们对战斗并不陌生，拥有属于自己的独特力量，称为“气力”。
过去，他们是自己家园的守护者，并且完美地融入了保护国。

^orange;食性^reset;：杂食性（浆果）

^orange;［天赋］^reset;
增益：能量值上限^green;+10%^reset;，能量回复速度^green;+8%^reset;，伤害^green;+5%^reset;，移动速度^green;+8%^reset;
抗性：寒冷抗性^green;+20%^reset;，暗影抗性^green;+25%^reset;，毒素抗性^green;+25%^reset;
狂怒光环（每当你造成伤害时，你会变得更加危险，伤害^green;+15%^reset;，防御^red;-10%^reset;）

^orange;［环境］^reset;
炎热生态：防御^red;-20%^reset;
丛林森林：能量值上限^green;+5%^reset;，击退抵抗^green;+10%^reset;

^orange;［武器］^reset;
手枪，自动手枪：伤害^green;+15%^reset;，能量值上限^green;+15%^reset;
短矛，矛：伤害^green;+8%^reset;，暴击几率^green;+5%^reset;
魔杖，法杖：伤害^green;+5%^reset;，暴击几率^green;+5%^reset;
拳套：伤害^green;+10%^reset;

^red;［弱点］^reset;
减益：生命值上限^red;-5%^reset;，防御^red;-5%^reset;,饥饿速度^red;+6%^reset;
抗性：辐射抗性^red;-30%^reset;，电系抗性^red;-30%^reset;，火焰抗性^red;-30%^reset;

Texts.Eng:
Despite their fluffy appearance, this species is incredibly adaptive. They are no strangers to fighting and have their own unique power named Aura. In past they were guardians of their home world, and merged perfectly with the Protectorate.

  ^orange;Diet^reset;: Omnivore (berries)

^orange;Perks^reset;:
  Energy x^green;1.1^reset;, Damage x^green;1.05^reset;, +^green;8^reset;% Speed
  ^green;Resist^reset;: +^green;20^reset;% Ice, +^green;50^reset;% Poison, +^green;25^reset;% Shadow
  Aura Berserk: Gain multipliers to Damage and Defense approaching (x^green;1.15^reset;, x^red;0.9^reset;) as your health decreases.

^orange;Weapons^reset;:
  Shortspear, Spear: Damage x^green;1.08^reset;, +^green;0.25^reset;% Crit Chance^reset;
  Wand, Staff: Damage x^green;1.05^reset;, Energy x^green;1.05^reset;
  Fist: Damage x^green;1.1^reset;
  (Machine) Pistol: Damage x^green;1.15^reset;, Energy x^green;1.15^reset;

^orange;Environment^reset;:
  Hot biomes: Defense x^red;0.9^reset;
  Jungle biomes: Energy x^green;1.05^reset;, +^green;10^reset;% Knockback Resistance

^red;Weaknesses^reset;:
  Health & Defense x^red;0.95^reset;
  +^red;6^reset;% Hunger Drain
  ^red;Resist^reset;: -^red;30^reset;% Fire, Electric & Radiation

Playstyle: ^yellow;Fighting^reset;
